title: DJ Yoda Goes To The Movies.avi
description:
In September 2005, DJ Yoda performed his first ground-breaking DVD scratch show to a packed out movie theatre in the heart of London.
The result is captured on this DVD.

Features:-

Star Wars, the Muppet Show, Beat Street, Tron, Gladiator, Big Trouble In Little China, The Wedding Singer, Rushmore, Back to the Future, Shogun Assassin, Beverly Hills Cop, Class of Nuke &#039;Em High, Crouching Tiger, Hidden Dragon, Transformers, Scarface, Nas - &#039;It Ain&#039;t Hard To Tell&#039;, the original Batman TV series, Enter The Dragon, Eddie Murphy routine, Don&#039;t Stop &#039;Til You Get Enough video, Old School, The Running Man, Texas Chainsaw Massacre, Gremlins, Titan A.E., Ghostbusters, Billie Jean music video, DMC winning sets, Kindergarten Cop, , Deliverance, O Brother, Where Art Thou?, Beavis and Butthead Do America, 

All mixed up and re-scored with plenty of classic funk and soul breaks, 80s classics, Roots Manuva, Dr. Dre, Snoop Dogg, Blackalicious, East Flatbush Project, Theme tunes, some electro, big beat, Chemical Brother&#039;s &#039;Push the Button&#039;.
